00:32:17.380 --> 00:32:19.296
No matter how many hours
you work, you're paid

00:32:19.296 --> 00:32:21.660
a minimum of eight.

00:32:21.660 --> 00:32:22.897
There's a swing pay bonus.

00:32:22.897 --> 00:32:24.730
So if you start your
day somewhere different

00:32:24.730 --> 00:32:26.980
than you end the day, then
you have to pay the person,

00:32:26.980 --> 00:32:31.690
I think, 30 minutes extra
for their driving time,

00:32:31.690 --> 00:32:34.180
or whatever, for getting
to the other location

00:32:34.180 --> 00:32:36.920
where you potentially
left your car.

00:32:36.920 --> 00:32:40.640
