just decreasing the off-peak
and not touching the peak.

00:44:04.300 --> 00:44:06.466
AUDIENCE: OK, but then, I
mean, proportionally, more

00:44:06.466 --> 00:44:07.820
of your hours are on the peak.

00:44:07.820 --> 00:44:08.800
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ:
Yes, exactly.

00:44:08.800 --> 00:44:09.680
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

00:44:09.680 --> 00:44:12.141
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ:
Exactly, yeah.

00:44:12.141 --> 00:44:12.640
All right--

00:44:12.640 --> 00:44:13.990
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

00:44:15.340 --> 00:44:17.780
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ:
So that was a good.

