01:10:34.880 --> 01:10:37.670
for problems in the schedule.

01:10:37.670 --> 01:10:39.700
So say I'm driving
out on this bus route.

01:10:39.700 --> 01:10:42.242
And it takes me eight minutes
longer than I thought it would.

01:10:42.242 --> 01:10:44.408
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ:
I wouldn't characterize it

01:10:44.408 --> 01:10:46.350
as a problem with the
schedule per se, but--

01:10:46.350 --> 01:10:48.890
so the schedule is a
